Package comp3111.rankingAlgo

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DR
    This class either calculates the rank of a name in a specified data set type/country/year (and gender) or works as a running rank tracker using Dense Ranking system
    LD
    Levenshtein distance, a method of calculating similarities between two strings (names).
    MCR
    This class either calculates the rank of a name in a specified data set type/country/year (and gender) or works as a running rank tracker using Modified Competition Ranking System NOTE THAT THIS FUNCTION DOES NOT SUPPORT ITERATORS
    OR
    This class either calculates the rank of a name in a specified data set type/country/year (and gender) or works as a running rank tracker using Ordinal Ranking System
    RankingAlgorithm
    super class for all algorithms
    RankingAlgorithmFactory
    Factory class used for different rank generation methods
    rankResolver
    Class holds different methods of resolving not found name in rank
    SCR
    This class either calculates the rank of a name in a specified data set type/country/year (and gender) or works as a running rank tracker using Standard Competition Ranking system
